NEWS
====

GET /news
---------
params:
	- aggregated = 1/0 (default = 0)
		- old = 1/0 (???)
	- offset = int (default 0)
	- limit = int (default 30)
	- oldestId = int

todos:
	- deprecate old stuff in v3, new GET /news defaults would be the parameters being passed now

notes:
	- requires authenticated user

GET /news/aggregated
--------------------
params:
	- offset = int (default 0)
	- limit = int (default 30)
	- oldestId = int (used for compatibility)

todos:
	- in v3, this will be moved to the top-level endpoint (GET /news)
	- better pagination (since/after, etc...)

notes:
	- requires authenticated user

POST /news/{id}/read
--------------------
mark news item(s) as read

params:
	- include_older = 1/0 (default 0)

notes:
	- still in use?
	- requires authenticated user